features: 【Nearly Natural Artificial Plants】The greenery decorations are made of friendly plastic material, and their exquisite craftsmanship and vibrant colors make them look like natural plants. Different Plants are mixed and matched to make the whole more lush and ornamental. Even at home, you can feel the green charm of nature and have a good mood.

【Minimalist Shell Pot】Our artificial greenery has quality cement shell pots, no need for you to add accessories. The old beige shell design adds a modern touch to the plants, providing you with a unique visual experience and enhancing the beauty of your home.

【Easy to Care】Unlike natural plants, our small fake plants require virtually no maintenance, no watering and pruning, and no sunlight. Even if you don't have time to care for them, they will remain vibrant for a long time. Just wipe them with a wet towel, they'll look brand new immediately.

【All-match Decoration】With a length of 7.87 in/ 20 cm, width of 3.54 in/ 9 cm and height of 5.9 in/ 15 cm, our artificial plants set of 2 are perfect for various situations. They can be great ornaments for your home, such as decorating desks, bookshelves, windowsills, garden tables, etc. They can also become the eye protection greenery in your office, helping relieve your anxiety in busy work.
【Perfect Gift Choice】Our succulent artificial plants are a delightful gift for your lover, friends, or families on Mother's Day, birthdays, anniversaries, or Easter, etc, conveying your deep love.
